messages.content: Ah hello! Oh I will hope to be in Bali soon! Thanks so much for reaching out. Loved coming across your work. Keep in touch! Xo JB
j_b_j_o_n_e_s wasn't notified about this message because they're in quiet mode.

Hey Jb! I want to say hi from across the internet & ocean and thank you for following our project. I hope we can cross paths soon, please reach out if you'll be in Bali soon and we'd love to have you over to the studio. & that calder necklace is one of the very best things ever! Sending love to you, xCarina
